OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FWith rain and brisk winds sweeping
OL,7,Fthrough many locations, it doesn't
OL,8,Freally feel like summer.
OL,10,FBut by this time next week, it'll be a
OL,11,Fvery different story.
OL,13,FThe details will become clearer in the
OL,14,Fnext few days, but come next week,
OL,15,Ftemperatures are looking like they'll
OL,16,Freach the high 20s, with even a hint
OL,17,Fof it reaching 30C.
OL,19,FWhat's in store in the next few days?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
