OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FThroughout Monday, cloudy skies with
OL,7,Frain are moving from west to east,
OL,8,Fwith some brisk winds creating a fresh
OL,9,Ffeel for the time of year.
OL,11,FIn the south-east, we can expect the
OL,12,Fchance of some thundery bursts later
OL,13,Fin the day. Brighter skies will
OL,14,Fdevelop from the west as the rain
OL,15,Fclears.
OL,17,FInto Tuesday, there is to be a clearer
OL,18,Fstart in the east and south-east.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
