PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FBursts of rain are expected in the
OL,7,Fwest - and they are to move to all
OL,8,Flocations through the day with fresh
OL,9,Fsouth-west winds.
OL,11,FThe heavier bursts will bring hail and
OL,12,Fthunder with a deluge in places and
OL,13,Ftemperatures will be below average for
OL,14,Fthe time of year.
OL,16,FThe disappointing conditions will keep
OL,17,Fus on our toes through the middle of
OL,18,Fthe week onwards.
OL,20,FIt's looking like rain on and off,
OL,21,Ftogether with brisk winds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
