PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FBut any sunnier breaks will be making
OL,7,Fall the difference as the sun at its
OL,8,Fstrongest at this time of year.
OL,10,FWhen are there signs of the weather
OL,11,Fchanging?
OL,13,FAfter low pressure systems dominated
OL,14,Four weather for the start of June -
OL,15,Fhigh pressure is showing signs of a
OL,16,Freturn next weekend.
OL,18,FAs the high pressure builds or
OL,19,Fstrengthens from the south, it will
OL,20,Fsettle down with calmer, drier and
OL,21,Fsunnier conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
