PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FTemperatures are expected to gradually
OL,7,Frecover and it won't take too long for
OL,8,Fit to become much warmer -
OL,9,Fparticularly from the south of
OL,10,FEngland, into the midlands and Wales.
OL,12,FEventually the warmth will become more
OL,13,Fwidespread and temperatures will be
OL,14,Fmuch higher for all of us through next
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FWhat temperatures can we expect?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
