PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FWith the sun at its strongest this
OL,7,Ftime of year we're expecting
OL,8,Ftemperatures to reach a maximum of 26-
OL,9,F27C on Saturday.
OL,11,FThen it is to be closer to 28C or more
OL,12,Fby Sunday.
OL,14,FThat's a very different feel for all
OL,15,Fof us - making it a good 10C or more
OL,16,Fhigher than the last few days.
OL,18,FInto next week there's a hint of
OL,19,Ftemperatures boosting closer to 30C
OL,20,Fand beyond - more likely so in the
OL,21,Fsouth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
