PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780953074
OL,3,CTemperatures to soar this weekend - is
OL,4,Canother heatwave brewing?
OL,6,FWith the heat there'll be a muggier
OL,7,Fand humid feel for some of us both by
OL,8,Fday and night, which brings a chance
OL,9,Fof heavy thundery downpours being
OL,10,Ftriggered.
OL,12,FFurther north the heat will be more
OL,13,Fmanageable and comfortable.
OL,15,FThe details will become clearer in the
OL,16,Fnext few days but - it'll feel a
OL,17,Flittle more like summer than it does
OL,18,Fright now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
